description: Triangle read by rows: T(n,d) = number of distinct properly d-dimensional polyominoes (or polycubes) with n cells (n >= 1,d>=0).
links: W. F. Lunnon, Counting multidimensional polyominoes. Computer Journal 18 (1975), no. 4, pp. 366-367.
author: Richard Schroeppel
extensions: Edited by _N. J. A. Sloane_, Sep 23 2011.
